υνεντεύξεις του καστ και του σκηνοθέτη για το πώς γυρίστηκε η δεύτερη σεζόν της δημοφιλούς σειράς."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: Making Season 2","runtime":28,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81922471","overview":"From set designs to character arcs, get exclusive cast and director interviews on how Season 2 of the globally most-watched series was brought to life."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game : Le making-of de la saison 2","runtime":27,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fr/title/81922471","overview":"Des interviews exclusives des acteurs et du réalisateur dévoilent ce qui a donné vie à la saison 2 de la série la plus regardée au monde, des décors à l'arc narratif des personnages."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Nyerd meg az életed: Így készült a 2. évad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81922471","overview":"A stábbal és a rendezővel készült exkluzív interjúkból a díszlettervektől a karakterfejlődésekig mindent megtudhatsz arról, hogy készült a világ legnézettebb sorozatának 2. évada."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: 2. Sezon - Kamera Arkası","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81922471","overview":"Dünya genelinde izlenme rekoru kıran dizinin 2. sezonunun, set tasarımlarından karakter öykülerine kadar nasıl hayata geçirildiğini oyuncuların ve yönetmenin ağzından dinleyin."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Documental que inclou entrevistes exclusives amb actors i directors sobre com van donar vida a la temporada 2 de la sèrie més vista del món, des de l'escenografia fins al desenvolupament del personatge."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"สควิดเกม เล่นลุ้นตาย: การสร้างซีซั่น 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/th/title/81922471","overview":"ตั้งแต่การออกแบบฉากไปจนถึงจุดเปลี่ยนของตัวละคร รับชมบทสัมภาษณ์สุดพิเศษจากนักแสดงและผู้กำกับที่จะมาพูดคุยเกี่ยวกับการสร้างซีซั่น 2 ของซีรีส์ที่มีผู้ชมสูงสุดทั่วโลก"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Así se hizo ‘El juego del calamar: Temporada 2'","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81922471","overview":"Desde la escenografía hasta el reparto, elenco y director de la serie más vista del mundo ofrecen entrevistas exclusivas sobre cómo se filmó la segunda temporada."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Jocul calamarului: Din culisele sezonului 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81922471","overview":"De la decoruri la evoluția personajelor, află cum a prins contur sezonul 2 al celui mai urmărit serial la nivel mondial. Interviuri exclusive cu actorii și regizorii."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Jak vznikala Hra na oliheň: Druhá řada","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81922471","overview":"Jak vznikaly jednotlivé scény a jak se vyvíjely postavy druhé řady nejsledovanějšího seriálu na světě? To vám v exkluzivních rozhovorech prozradí samotní herci i režisér."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Making Squid Game - Staffel 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81922471","overview":"Vom Setdesign bis zur Entwicklung der Figuren: Die Stars und der Regisseur berichten exklusiv, wie Staffel 2 der weltweiten Erfolgsserie zum Leben erweckt wurde."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"لعبة الحبّار: كواليس موسم 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81922471","overview":"من تصميم مواقع التصوير إلى تطوير الشخصيات، استمتع بمشاهدة مقابلات حصرية مع الممثلين والمُخرجين حول تصوير الموسم الثاني من المسلسل الأكثر مشاهدة على مستوى العالم."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"لعبة الحبّار: كواليس موسم 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81922471","overview":"من تصميم مواقع التصوير إلى تطوير الشخصيات، استمتع بمشاهدة مقابلات حصرية مع الممثلين والمُخرجين حول تصوير الموسم الثاني من المسلسل الأكثر مشاهدة على مستوى العالم."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"魷魚遊戲：第 2 季：製作特輯","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81922471","overview":"從場景設計到角色發展，透過演員群與導演的獨家訪談，一窺這部全球收視冠軍影集的第 2 季如何製作。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"鱿鱼游戏：第 2 季制作花絮","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81922471","overview":"观看独家演员和导演采访，从场景设计到人物的转变，了解这部全球最受欢迎剧集的第 2 季是如何搬上荧幕的。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"魷魚遊戲：第 2 季：製作特輯","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81922471","overview":"從場景設計到角色發展，透過演員群與導演的獨家訪談，一窺這部全球收視冠軍影集的第 2 季如何製作。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Igra lignje: Iza kulisa 2. sezone","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81922471","overview":"Pogledaj ekskluzivne intervjue u kojima glumci i redatelj komentiraju scenografiju i razvoj likova te otkrivaju kako je nastala 2. sezona najgledanije serije na svijetu."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: Bag kulisserne på sæson 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81922471","overview":"Få eksklusive interviews med skuespillere og instruktører om, hvordan sæson 2 af verdens mest sete serie blev bragt til live, lige fra scenografi til karakterudvikling."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: Making Season 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81922471","overview":"Exclusieve interviews met de cast en de regisseur over hoe seizoen 2 van de wereldwijd meest bekeken serie tot leven werd gebracht, van decorontwerp tot karakterontwikkeling."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: Näin tehtiin kausi 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81922471","overview":"Ohjaaja, näyttelijät ja työryhmä kertovat niin lavastesuunnittelusta kuin hahmotarinoistakin ja paljastavat, miten maailman katsotuimman sarjan kakkoskausi syntyi."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Le jeu du calmar : La revue de tournage de la saison 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81922471","overview":"Profitez d'entrevues avec la distribution et le réalisateur sur la création, des décors aux arcs narratifs, de la deuxième saison de la série la plus visionnée au monde."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"משחק הדיונון: מאחורי הקלעים של עונה 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81922471","overview":"ראיונות בלעדיים עם הבמאי וצוות השחקנים, שמספרים כיצד הפיחו חיים בעונה השנייה של הסדרה הנצפית ביותר בעולם – מעיצוב התפאורה ועד לסיפורי הדמויות."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: मेकिंग सीज़न 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81922471","overview":"दुनिया की सबसे ज़्यादा देखी जाने वाली सीरीज़ के सीज़न 2 की कास्ट और डायरेक्टर के एक्सक्लूसिव इंटरव्यू देखें और जानें सेट डिज़ाइन से लेकर किरदारों तक की कहानियां."},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: Making Season 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81922471","overview":"Dari desain set hingga pengembangan karakter dibahas dalam wawancara eksklusif dengan pemeran dan sutradara tentang pembuatan Season 2 serial terpopuler di dunia ini."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game - Stagione 2: dietro le quinte","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81922471","overview":"Dalla scenografia agli archi narrativi dei personaggi, guarda le interviste esclusive a cast e regista sulla realizzazione della seconda stagione della serie più vista al mondo."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"イカゲーム: シーズン2の舞台裏","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81922471","overview":"歴代最高の大ヒットを記録したシリーズのシーズン2はいかにして作られたか。セットデザインからキャラクターアークまで、キャストと監督の独占インタビューを通して制作の舞台裏に迫る。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/title/81922471","overview":"《오징어 게임》 시즌 2의 치열했던 제작 현장 속으로. 웅장한 세트장부터 캐릭터들의 이야기가 완성되는 순간까지, 전 세계를 매료한 드라마의 주역들이 들려주는 특별한 제작 비화."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Squid Game: Making Season 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81922471","overview":"Ikuti wawancara eksklusif bersama pelakon dan pengarah tentang penghasilan siri dengan tonton