 obliterate the cities for hundreds of miles around.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6138,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/9xjSHm0R9tII8JCWHS1VdbftFk1.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-28","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/xtnfoFs9vOLBF7Ox13mFmFUovey.jpg","original_title":"The Twisters","original_language":"en"},{"id":1214667,"adult":false,"title":"Making Squid Game: The Challenge","video":false,"overview":"Go behind the scenes and witness how the \"Squid Game\"-inspired reality show transformed from a scripted drama to a cutthroat, nail-biting competition.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5453,"vote_count":227,"poster_path":"/78yTLvtsMntVN1cLfzBuZj870pe.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-06","vote_average":7.96,"backdrop_path":"/i9bhxhUBFZHorvK81GNKMJGj2Kt.jpg","original_title":"Making Squid Game: The Challenge","original_language":"en"},{"id":1029235,"adult":false,"title":"Azrael","video":false,"overview":"In a world where no one speaks, a devout female hunts down a young woman who has escaped her imprisonment. Recaptured by its ruthless leaders, Azrael is due to be sacrificed to pacify an ancient evil deep within the surrounding wilderness.","genre_ids":[28,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3642,"vote_count":392,"poster_path":"/qpdFKDvJS7oLKTcBLXOaMwUESbs.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-27","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/np58LPJkwC3THsKBkBscDKSlQPz.jpg","original_title":"Azrael","original_language":"en"},{"id":926670,"adult":false,"title":"Henry Danger: The Movie","video":false,"overview":"Henry Hart meets a superfan—eager to fight crime with Kid Danger—who comes into possession of a device that can open up alternate realities. Facing a wild ride, Henry will need his best friend Jasper and his new superfan sidekick to find his way out or be stuck in another dimension forever.","genre_ids":[28,35,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.8243,"vote_count":250,"poster_path":"/dFWj2rOGsqSIX1PHFghbCBgpMnk.jpg",