6.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Making of 'The Terminator': A Retrospective","original_language":"en"},{"id":3161,"adult":false,"title":"Making Frankensense of Young Frankenstein","video":false,"overview":"Via reminiscences from writer/actor Gene Wilder and others, this documentary recalls the making of the 1974 film Young Frankenstein.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.3721,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/5PGLvCGG2B5MrtSf3VWlb9P9Kls.jpg","release_date":"1996-01-01","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Making Frankensense of Young Frankenstein","original_language":"en"},{"id":656663,"adult":false,"title":"Jackass Forever","video":false,"overview":"The Jackass crew, along with some newcomers, returns for one final round of hilarious, absurd, and dangerous stunts.","genre_ids":[28,35,99],"popularity":1.2479,"vote_count":881,"poster_path":"/ruHDFumJfW7F2vEqTZEQQ9xT7CA.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-01","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/f2J8DpT5bqV0AiI9VVcfiuqKo5l.jpg","original_title":"Jackass Forever","original_language":"en"},{"id":656693,"adult":false,"title":"The Making of Fallout: New Vegas","video":false,"overview":"This 8-part documentary includes behind the scenes interviews, concept art, and promotional trailers for the game.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.3951,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/AhgErLIX5jVuMgfIAe8cZBbIM0z.jpg","release_date":"2010-10-19","vote_average":8.7,"backdrop_path":"/m5bVosZPa0NvOXaph3Q0o8MzMQR.jpg","original_title":"The Making of Fallout: New Vegas","original_language":"en"},{"id":1458882,"adult":false,"title":"Making Megaforce","video":false,"overview":"He wanted to make a documentary about the making of Megaforce, one of 1982’s biggest box office failures. But when he met his hero, Megaforce star Barry “Ace Hunter” Bostwick, things started to get really out of hand.  Hal Needham’s big budget epic Megaforce was one of the undisputed worst movies of 1982, and beyond- a box office flop that time would like to forget. But there is one man who remembers …Bob Lindenmayer, and he’s on a quest to convince the rest of the world just how awesome this stunt-filled spectacle is.  As Bob delves into the movie’s history with cast and crew, he drags his childhood hero Barry Bostwick into his mission to relive the past. It’s a touching and hilarious tribute to the power of heroes, friendship, and flying motorcycles.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.5931,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/o6Bnqj5AHiNECKGcMZb8dgEiAeW.jpg","release_date":"2026-02-04","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/a27eN9fjmSel0SiqBKP2OX5phLJ.jpg","original_title":"Making Megaforce","original_language":"en"},{"id":1065302,"adult":false,"title":"Robin Hood: The Myth, the Man, the Movie","video":false,"overview":"U.S. network TV special surveying the history of Robin Hood in popular culture, emphasizing the 1991 film \"Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves\". Interviews with principal cast and crew from that film highlight the special. Pierce Brosnan hosts.","genre_ids":[99,10770],"popularity":0.4354,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/3ddJx6EHDrxNpXzSAqGPe9Cnjzn.jpg","release_date":"1991-06-13","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Robin Hood: The Myth, the Man, the Movie","original_language":"en"},{"id":470035,"adult":false,"title":"Spider-Man 2: Making the Amazing","video":false,"overview":"A comprehensive 12-part documentary on the making of \"Spider-Man 2,\" covering everything from pre-production to premiere.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,99],"popularity":0.5397,"vote_count":80,"poster_path":"/3oF3GbxSSQxO9rWjrUjwAFi1fSF.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-30","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Spider-Man 2: Making the Amazing","original_language":"en"},{"id":1263614,"adult":false,"title":"Karl May's Orient-Filme: Making-of","video":false,"overview":"Featurette about the filming of Durchs wilde Kurdistan and Der Schut","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1489,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"relea